Package hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttachmentHolder<T>
    Classes can implement this interface in order to allow Objects to be attached to its instances.
    DrawPrioritizeable<T>
    Represents something that can be drawn in an environment where overlapping might happen.
    IodineGui
    Represents a GUI (General User Interface) that can be opened for players who are in the IodinePlayer.State#MODDED state.
    IodineGui.ClosedAction
    The handler of the closed action.
    IodineOverlay
    Represents an overlay that can be opened for players who are in the IodinePlayer.State#MODDED state.
    IodineRoot<T extends IodineRoot<T>>
    Represents a IodineGui or a IodineOverlay.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuiElements<T extends GuiElement<T>>
    The GuiElements that can be added to GUIs.
    IodineColor
    An immutable class representing an ARGB color.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IodineOverlay.Anchor
    Represents positions to which overlays can be anchored.
